00:42:28,535 --> 00:42:30,634
That flag is
our proud Southern history.

608
00:42:30,636 --> 00:42:33,204
It might be your proud
Southern history, C.P.,

609
00:42:33,206 --> 00:42:35,039
but it sure as hell
