666
00:47:40,783 --> 00:47:42,318
- Miles.
- Miles.

667
00:47:43,052 --> 00:47:45,219
What year did you
just finish, Miles?

668
00:47:45,221 --> 00:47:46,854
- My junior year.
- Mm-hmm.

669
00:47:46,856 --> 00:47:48,958
